Alembic Database Migrations for Planted
========================================

This directory contains Alembic database migration scripts for the Planted garden management application.

Quick Start
-----------

Check current migration version:
    $ alembic current

Apply all pending migrations:
    $ alembic upgrade head

Rollback the last migration:
    $ alembic downgrade -1

Create a new migration:
    $ alembic revision -m "Description of changes"

For detailed documentation, see:
    docs/database_migrations.md

Important
---------
Always backup your database before running migrations!
Use the provided backup script:
    $ ./scripts/backup_database.sh

Directory Structure
-------------------
alembic/
├── versions/           # Migration scripts (auto-generated)
├── env.py             # Runtime environment configuration
├── script.py.mako     # Template for new migrations
└── README             # This file

Migration files in versions/ should never be modified after being applied to production.